lass=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求救"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T15:55:31.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=ilbAUjjR90mprNH%2BEJ%2FAJgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=bd35ec50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】基斯坦奴朗拿度周六正式在意甲登場，不過英國球迷卻無法收看賽事頭15分鐘，或會錯過C朗在意甲首個入波！<br />\n<br />\n今晚基斯坦奴朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）帶領祖雲達斯作客基爾禾，賽事在英國會由Eleven Sports頻道直播，頻道的fb更會免費直播，無奈根據英國足總的規定，每逢球季周六下午2:45至5:15是直播真空期，期間禁止電視上或網上足球直播，換言之祖記賽事的頭15分鐘英國球迷無緣欣賞。<br />\n<br />\n英足總這條規例實行超過50年，當初是為了保障本地賽事的入場觀眾數字，但時移世易，規定惹來不少人士抨擊。<br />\n<br />\n雖然賽事頭15分鐘電視畫面會全黑，但會有現場評述，英國球迷屆時只得豎起耳朵收聽C朗的地標戰。<br />\n<br />\n應該係因為咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7582929d1088ad6021bf17d476f85f385a22e6bd","tid":784733,"uid":45189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T15:56:18.000Z","msg":"要開波了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9318e6b0f0209f0aea6ad0bbfd02c38b49e7f01","tid":784733,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T15:57:14.000Z","msg":"link呢你老母"},{"pid":"beb90ed325caa308610f02540869980fa9c49058","tid":784733,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cbd479f390c29f2836d899668e27adb3f8f8a3a","tid":784733,"uid":45189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T15:27:31.000Z","msg":"Kick off time:12:00<br />\n<br />\n基爾禾<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/232443_a7c0ef76bfedf8f167ac60f3b326639d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F232443_a7c0ef76bfedf8f167ac60f3b326639d.png&h=f3a2e70a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n祖雲達斯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/18/232545_f4e277656260f1c7791a7d788b2130ac.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F18%2F232545_f4e277656260f1c7791a7